/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			**************THIS IS WORK IN PROGRESS****************

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
16 January 2013	cnwndl1	Initial creation
11 May 2018	jlgrs1	make delete Terminal work
23/07/2019	jlgka1 	TFS 45620	JMT - Refactor remove remaining  Voyage Commodity  Planning
*/

vars

